# --- GLOBAL DATA PROTECTION ---
# These are blocked everywhere EXCEPT where whitelisted below
*.parquet
*.csv
*.sql
*.dump

# --- DAY 01: FULL TRANSPARENCY ---
# (Nothing is ignored here; Day 1 is your public demo area)

# --- DAY 02: GEOMETRY PROTECTION ---
